You can use chai assertions and mocha test library. 

You can also do unit testing in solidity and integration testing with javascript.
But with javascript and truffle you can do both unit and integration testing. 

Read on https://blog.bancor.network/this-analysis-of-bancor-is-flawed-18ab8a000d43
